## Xcode
#
# .DS_Store is a file that contains the attributes of a folder or a build volume's folder,
# such as the position of icons, background picture, and so on.
# macOS: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/.DS_Store

.DS_Store

# Xcode
#
# gitignore contents: https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Global/Xcode.gitignore

## Xcode Workspace
#
# https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Swift.gitignore
# https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Global/macOS.gitignore

*.xcworkspace
!*.xcworkspace/contents.xcworkspacedata
!*.xcworkspace/xcshareddata/
!*.xcworkspace/xcshareddata/swiftpm/

## Xcode 15+ new default ignore list
**/.xcshareddata/
!**/.xcshareddata/*.xcscmblueprint
!**/.xcshareddata/*.xcworkspacedata

## IDE
#
# Xcode 15+ default ignores
*.xcscmblueprint
*.xcworkspacedata
**/.xcworkspacedata
!**/.xcworkspacedata/*.xcworkspacedata

## Settings
#
# .xcuserstate is a file that contains the state of the current Xcode window.
# It is auto-generated and should not be tracked by Git.
**/.xcuserstate
**/*.xcuserstate

